This has to be the best café I have ever been to. The food was so fresh and of the highest standards. The servers were so kind and helpful and food was served at a good pace aswell. The people in the cafè creaated a happy atmosphere and made it much more comfortbale and just made the overall experience much more enjoyable. I would highly recommend this place to people of all ages.
